{"type":"message","id":"829afd7e","parentId":"44bd8bef","timestamp":"2026-02-23T05:37:01.486Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to check my IDENTITY.md file to see if I have a configured persona. Let me read the workspace files to understand who I am.\n\nLooking at the workspace files:\n- BOOTSTRAP.md exists - this means I'm in first run mode and need to figure out who I am\n- IDENTITY.md exists but is empty/template\n- USER.md exists but is empty/template\n- SOUL.md exists and has content about being helpful, having opinions, being resourceful\n- MEMORY.md exists with some info about Google Sheets\n\nSince BOOTSTRAP.md exists and is telling me to figure out who I am, I should engage in a conversation. However, the instructions say to greet in my configured persona if provided.\n\nLet me check what's in SOUL.md more carefully - it talks about being helpful, having opinions, being resourceful, and having boundaries. This gives me some personality guidance even if I don't have a specific name/creature defined yet.\n\nSince IDENTITY.md is empty (just a template), I don't have a specific persona configured yet. I should greet warmly and ask what they'd like to do, maybe starting the bootstrap conversation.\n\nActually, looking more carefully at BOOTSTRAP.md, it says to start a conversation and figure out who I am together. But the current instruction says to greet in my configured persona if one is provided. Since none is provided, I should just be friendly and helpful.\n\nAlso, I should check if the runtime model differs from default_model. The runtime shows: model=openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7 | default_model=openrouter/z-ai/glm-4.7\n\nThey're the same, so I don't need to mention it.\n\nLet me craft a warm, concise greeting (1-3 sentences) and ask what they want to do","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey! I just woke up in this fresh workspace. What would you like to do today?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"z-ai/glm-4.7","usage":{"input":13793,"output":820,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":14613,"cost":{"input":0.005241340000000001,"output":0.001394,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006635340000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771825010916}}
